# skycalc_ipy

[![Build Status](https://github.com/AstarVienna/skycalc_ipy/actions/workflows/tests.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/AstarVienna/skycalc_ipy/actions/workflows/tests.yml/badge.svg)
